
* Camel
*** components 
*** CBR (content based routing)

      from("jms:incomingOrders") 
      .choice()
          .when(header("CamelFileName").endsWith(".xml"))
              .to("jms:xmlOrders")
          .when(header("CamelFileName").regex("^.*(csv|csl)$"))
              .to("jms:csvOrders")
          .otherwise()
              .to("jms:badOrders") 
              .stop()
      .end()
      .to(...)
*** Multicast / parallel

      ExecutorService executor = Executors.newFixedThreadPool(16);

      from("jms:xmlOrders")
      .wireTap("jms:orderAudit") // pass through message, w/side effect (send to a queue for logging)
        .multicast()
        .stopOnException()     // needs error handling setup
        .parallelProcessing()  // 
        .executorService(executor) // change thread handling
      .to("jms:accounting", "jms:production");


*** Marshalling java object to/from xml:
      from(..)
      .marshal.xstream
      ....
      .unmarshal.xstream
      .to(...)


